    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 engineering. The naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six remains internally pristine, featuring a recently serviced double-VANOS system and verified rod bearing clearances. Power is managed via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential with a 3.62 final drive ratio. Crucially, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to mitigate structural fatigue, ensuring the chassis handles high lateral G-loads with factory-fresh rigidity. With zero deferred maintenance and a documented service history, this is a turnkey specimen for the collector who demands mechanical perfection and telepathic handling dynamics.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
